<p>My wife and I would like to invest in gold and/or silver.  Are there 1. Sales taxes on the purchase of these metals?, and 2. Are there capital gains taxes that must be paid on these investments?  In summary, what are the tax laws and liabilities which come into play if we invest in and start compiling a horde of Silver Eagles?</p>
